  "instructions": [
    "thread lamb meat onto metal skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "in a small bowl, mix together panang paste, soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic, peppercorns, and salt.",
    "brush the lamb skewers with olive oil and sprinkle with coriander and paprika.",
    "place the lamb skewers in the air fryer basket, leaving a little space between each skewer.",
    "set the air fryer to 400 degrees fahrenheit for 12 minutes, shaking halfway through."
